gamere:Praia rdf:type owl:Class ;
             rdfs:label "Praia" .


###  http://example.org/def/gamere#Provincia
gamere:Provincia rdf:type owl:Class ;
                 rdfs:label "Provincia" .


###  http://example.org/def/gamere#Ubicacion
